quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  62,9,"You who believe, when you are called for the mandatory prayer of the Friday, then hurry up to God's remembrance, stopping the trade. That is better for you if only you knew"
  62,10,"Then when the mandatory prayer is finished, disperse in the land and look for God's bounty, and remember God often, so that you may be successful"
  62,11,"And when they see a business or an amusement, they go away to it and leave you standing. Say: what is with God is better than the amusement and the business, and God is the best of the providers"